Carnage/Teltoli

* Teltoli stretched and yawned, she was full and SO tired!
It had only been a click and 1/2 since they had found this beach shore and 
she listened to the rolling of the waves, they were calming to the soul. 
Teltoli looked over at Carnage and smiled at what she saw...*

Teltoli: " Silly thing!"

* She watched as Carnage slept on her back, Teltoli thought that she looked 
like a dog waiting for someone to scratch it's belly. She snickered and 
smiled before laying her head on her paws, it had been a fun day.
Teltoli's smile widened even further as Carnage rolled onto her side with a 
loud...THUMP! Now the Fuzor only saw the back of the brown and black 
reptile, she sighed and closed her eyes...she would sleep well.
Carnage, on the other hand, withered and writhed in her sleep. The memories 
were back and with a fierce vengeance now that Carnage wasn't awake and 
couldn't just push them back in the depths of her memory, they came to the 
surface and spilled forth in one terrifying nightmare!
Everything came to the surface, the destruction of her home world, the 
Predacons taking her in and teaching her how to kill, her friendship with 
Dinobot,and finally his....death! Everything!*
